      <title>国债收益率从上周高点回落，延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/treasuries-extend-rally-as-yields-retreat-from-last-week-s-peaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债券市场预期在年底最后一天将出现买盘，美国国债周一上涨，扭转了近期的跌势。]]></description>
